---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import impactImage from '../assets/scorecard.png';
---

<section class="bg-primary-darkGreen py-20" id="course">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <Image 
          src={impactImage} 
          alt="Scorecard for Milt's Golf Center Par 3 Course" 
          class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full"
          width={600}
          height={400}
        />
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-primary-white mb-6">
          Course Information
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-white">
          Milt's Golf Center features a beautiful Par 3 course that is perfect for golfers of all skill levels. Whether you're a beginner looking to practice your short game or an experienced golfer wanting to work on your accuracy, our Par 3 course offers a fun and challenging experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
